data.description: VA Acquired property being sold in "AS IS" condition and price has been discounted accordingly. Located in a very nice neighborhood featuring 4 bedrooms, 1 3/4 Baths and 2 car attached garage. Large, fenced backyard for the children and pets to play. This property may qualify for Seller Financing (Vendee). Home was built prior to 1978 and the possibility of lead base paint potentially exists. Central Heat and Air for seasonal comfort. Inground storm cellar for family safety during the storm season. Kitchen has Bay window and nice cabinets. Home will need only minor cosmetic upgrades. Call the listing agent, Larry Liter at Parks-Jones Realty, 580-695-2033, for additional information and private showing appointment.
